ISLAMABAD, Feb 1 (APP):Chief of the Army Staff General Qamar Javed Bajwa Monday called on Prime Minister Imran Khan here.
The matters pertaining to internal and external security were discussed during the meeting, which was also attended by Inter-Services Intelligence Director General Lt General Faiz Hamid, a PM Office press release said.
